WEBVTT

00:01.846 --> 00:03.812
<i>Previously on</i> Legend
of the Seeker.

00:04.557 --> 00:06.523
The only way to close the
rift is the way the Creator

00:06.524 --> 00:08.559
sealed the Underworld.
The Stone of Tears.

00:08.560 --> 00:10.326
I think it's a compass.

00:10.327 --> 00:11.794
This orb will guide
the Seeker's way.

00:11.795 --> 00:13.561
To what? Hopefully
the Stone of Tears.

00:13.562 --> 00:15.595
Richard, we can't trust her.

00:15.596 --> 00:18.196
Twice now she's proven
herself to me. I can use her.

00:18.197 --> 00:19.664
I consider you to be my friend.

00:21.378 --> 00:22.445
I save Richard.

00:23.529 --> 00:25.129
Suddenly you wanna
defeat the Keeper?

00:25.447 --> 00:26.514
I want to live again.

00:30.617 --> 00:31.751
<i>Sister Marianna,</i>

00:31.752 --> 00:34.385
<i>Darken Rahl has betrayed me.</i>

00:34.386 --> 00:35.785
What do you ask of us?

00:35.786 --> 00:37.586
<i>Send him back to me.</i>

00:37.587 --> 00:39.788
I have no intention of going back.

00:39.789 --> 00:42.119
The only reason you
want to save the world

00:42.120 --> 00:43.119
is to save yourself.

00:45.223 --> 00:47.724
I'm sure I'll see you again,
brother.

00:47.725 --> 00:48.758
I'm sure you will.

00:51.727 --> 00:56.396
<i>Richard Cypher, you are the
true Seeker.</i>

